ConnectApi Rate Limit Changes for New Orgs

To avoid potentially restrictive per user, per namespace, per hour ConnectApi rate limits, method calls from orgs created in Summer â€™24 and later count toward the per org, per 24-hour Salesforce Platform API rate limit. For these new orgs, only method calls that require Chatter are subject to the per user, per namespace, per hour rate limit.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience, Salesforce Classic, and all versions of the Salesforce mobile app in all editions in all API versions.
